org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet

类 FileRunnable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet.FileRunnable
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class FileRunnable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    FileRunnable creates new Thread for reading file and simulating values in the file. Implementation of Runnable class is necessary to avoid blocking of GUI thread.
    作者:
    Josip Balic

      • FileRunnable

        public FileRunnable(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> dateTime,
                    java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> simulation,
                    java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> time2,
                    java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> values2,
                    long[] time4,
                    TelnetServer telnetServer,
                    java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Integer> places)
        Constructor for FileRunnable class. Here we initialize all the variables.
        参数:
        dateTime - , ArrayList that contains date and time of simulations.
        simulation - , ArrayList that contains type of simulations.
        time2 - , ArrayList that contains time of events.
        values2 - , ArrayList that contains values in certain times.
        time4 - , long[] that contains time of events converted to long milliseconds.
        telnetServer - , TelnetServer through which we send battery values to emulator.
        places - , ArrayList that contains places when second time date is reached.
